---
title: Blueberry Double Turkey Burgers with Rosemary Potato Coins and Mustard Aioli
description: These turkey burgers smothered in blueberry jam, mustard aioli and melty cheddar cheese check all the right flavour boxes! The earthy rosemary roasted potatoes provide a lovely complementary flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221019_R1010_W01_CA_KB_Main_low-2720cbf3.jpg
